Subject: drm/i915: s/num_active_crtcs/num_active_pipes/
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: c08e91323920ec4b3a4d889af3988e300b1902f1
